    "body": "Hm, looks like I'm seeing this again, but only for test files. When using `-w` or `-w --run-all`, changes to my `src/` contracts are detected, but not modifications to my `test/` contracts are not detected. \r\n\r\nPossible factors:\r\n- I have the `test/` folder at the repo root, not nested within `src/`\r\n- In `foundry.toml` I have `remappings = [\"test/=test/\"]` so I can import test contracts using an absolute path instead of a relative path, e.g. `import \"test/utils/SomeUtil.sol\"`",
